## 2026-06-06 — Swift UI P3 cleanup follow-up (Codex)

Codex continued the broad review-remediation goal on branch
`fix/ui-p3-cleanups` in worktree `.worktrees/ui-p3-cleanups`.

Scope closed:
- `CommandPaletteView` now mirrors the existing search-page concurrency shape:
  query changes cancel the previous task, wait 300 ms, then run one service
  search or local fallback path, with cancellation guards before publishing
  results. A read-only subagent review caught that the first pass still entered
  local fallback after a cancelled service call; the final code exits before
  starting fallback work.
- `LiveSessionCard.elapsedText` and `ReplayState.densityBuckets` now reuse
  static `ISO8601DateFormatter` instances instead of allocating a formatter
