  runStartupBackfills + drainStartupIndexJobs; IndexJobRunner.runRecoverableJobsOnce
  (single batch); EngramServiceRunner runs structural scan in one gated command
  then drains FTS one batch per gated command. indexAll itself still holds the
  gate (inherent to single-writer model) — only the FTS-drain tail is bounded.
